{"tid":2323554,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"受試者出現神經問題 秘魯暫停中國疫苗試驗","createTime":"2020-12-13T09:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T14:44:20.000Z","uid":76310,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"481c762ab82b4de8d8e93787a632e9a73e94a7e9","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"受試者出現神經問題 秘魯暫停中國疫苗試驗<br />\n<br />\n秘魯國立衛生研究院今天表示，在一名受試者在接受中國國營的國藥集團疫苗接種後， 出現手臂難以活動的情況，院方決定暫停這支疫苗的試驗。 美聯社<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/12/12/98/9271451.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F12%2F12%2F98%2F9271451.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=cb12b0b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dc77db6c5d052a168c0dbefc881ecf625ab6df4","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"777同公墓員, 藍絲, 黑警, 廢老, 快D打<br />\n<br />\n出現手臂難以活動的情況, 即係癱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4523397968ba05b4c24a96537a90f29dbf609db","tid":2323554,"uid":289723,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"出年用香港人繼續測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4615d9d5e62a74de8b1ddeba78ab67f388b38220","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:08:33.000Z","msg":"秘魯當局在國內對中國國營的國藥集團（Sinopharm）2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫苗試驗中，發現一名受試者出現神經問題的情況後，已經暫停這項疫苗的臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體報導，秘魯國立衛生研究院（NationalInstitute of Health，INS）今天表示，在一名受試者出現手臂難以活動的情況後，院方決定暫停這支疫苗的試驗。<br />\n<br />\n首席研究員馬拉加（German Malaga）在記者會上表示：「我們幾天前依要求告知監管當局，我們（試驗中）有一名受試者出現神經症狀，可能符合一種名為吉蘭-巴雷氏症候群（Guillain-Barre syndrome）的症狀。」吉蘭-巴雷氏症候群是一種罕見、非感染性的神經病變，會影響手腳四肢的活動。<br />\n<br />\n中國國藥集團在秘魯的疫苗臨床試驗受試者約1萬2000人，原定在本週結束。<br />\n<br />\n如果這支疫苗試驗成功，秘魯政府預計將購買最多2000萬劑疫苗，提供國內2/3人口接種。這項疫苗試驗成功與否，要到2021年年中後才會知曉。<br />\n<br />\n全球約6萬人已經接種國藥集團的疫苗，其中包括在阿根廷、俄羅斯和沙烏地阿拉伯等國的受試者。<br />\n<br />\n秘魯是全球染疫人均死亡率最高國家之一，截至今天已有3萬6499人病逝、97萬9111人染疫。秘魯經濟受到疫情重創，第2季國內生產毛額（GDP）大幅萎縮逾30%。"},{"pid":"bd52e913d90ed2dcb7db955a5ac4a4e112d6cfeb","tid":2323554,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc77db6c5d052a168c0dbefc881ecf625ab6df4","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"777同公墓員, 藍絲, 黑警, 廢老, 快D打<br />\n<br />\n出現手臂難以活動的情況, 即係癱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"打疫苗打到神經系統出問題係好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e9d4657b2d345fd19aeed80e2774b82b56a59a","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:09:10.000Z","msg":"秘魯國立衛生研究院今天表示，在一名受試者在接受中國國營的國藥集團疫苗接種後， 出現手臂難以活動的情況，院方決定暫停這支疫苗的試驗。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F12%2F12%2F98%2F9271451.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&amp;h=cb12b0b4&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"f10efdd9bf2a291488b0f5d96c1fc732e569c558","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd52e913d90ed2dcb7db955a5ac4a4e112d6cfeb","tid":2323554,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc77db6c5d052a168c0dbefc881ecf625ab6df4","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"777同公墓員, 藍絲, 黑警, 廢老, 快D打<br />\n<br />\n出現手臂難以活動的情況, 即係癱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"打疫苗打到神經系統出問題係好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"好閒者<br />\n平時強国人都係咁"},{"pid":"5036673fc1c225107ca48b4b3d055f8fbacd76be","tid":2323554,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cddc4cda77dbf3bba4a0e79c843b17e2db44776","tid":2323554,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:24:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c64d2685c6cf747c6222d7c90be63ed4ffe06fb","tid":2323554,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"樓主學車未？"}]}